<h1> Edit <%= @figure.name %> </h1>

<form action="/figures/<%= @figure.id %>" method='POST'>


Choose a Landmark: <br>
<% Landmark.all.each do |landmark| %>
  <input type="checkbox" name= "figure[landmark_ids][]" id = "landmark_<%= landmark.id %>" value= "<%= landmark.id %>" <%= checked="checked" if @figure.landmark_ids.include?(landmark.id) %>>  <%= landmark.name %> <br>
<% end %> <br>

Choose a Title: <br>
<% Title.all.each do |title| %>
<input type="checkbox" name= "figure[title_ids][]"  id = "title_<%= title.id %>" value= "<%= title.id %>"> <%= title.name %> <br>
<% end %> <br>

Or...<br>


Edit Name: <br>

<input type='text' placeholder="Edit the name"  id = 'figure_name' name='figure[name]' />

Add Landmark: <br>

<input type='text' placeholder="Enter a new Landmark name..."  id = 'new_landmark' name='new_landmark[name]' />
<input type='text' placeholder="Enter the year it was created" name = 'new_landmark[year_completed]' /> <br>

Create a new Title: <br>


<input type='text' placeholder="Enter a new Title..." id = 'new_title' name='new_title[name]' />

<input type='submit' value="Edit Figure" />
</form>
